				<div id="post-590" class="hentry p5 post publish author-canuckaholic category-work-examples untagged is-full comments-closed pings-closed y2011 m05 d15 h13 slug-countrywide-communications"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://popdigital.ca/2011/05/15/countrywide-communications/" title="Permalink to Website: Countrywide Communications" rel="bookmark">Website: Countrywide Communications</a></h2>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">By </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://popdigital.ca/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Adrian">Adrian</a></span><span class="meta-sep meta-sep-entry-date"> | </span><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-entry-date">Published: </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-05-15T20:59:46-0700">May 15, 2011</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
					<div class="entry-content">
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-594" title="countrycomm_558x300" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/countrycomm_558x300.gif" alt="Countrywide Communications" width="558" height="300" /></p>
<h2>About:</h2>
<p>Countrywide Communications is a TELUS reseller partner with two stores in Maple Ridge. For this project we redesigned their website and set up the phones and rate plans to be displayed on the site from a dynamic data feed. The dynamic content was set up by reading in XML feeds provided by TELUS, parsing the data into a database, and displaying the resulting content on the site.</p>
<h2>Type of Project:</h2>
<p>Website. Underlying server architecture is LAMP. CMS is WordPress.</p>
<h2>URL:</h2>
<p><a title="Countrywide Communications" href="http://countrywidecommunications.com/" target="_blank">countrywidecommunications.com</a></p>
<h2>What We Did:</h2>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>HTML/XHTML</li>
<li>CSS</li>
<li>PHP</li>
<li>Javascript</li>
<li>jQuery</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>Graphic Design</li>
<li>Database</li>
<li>WordPress</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearFloats"></div>
<div class="tweetthis" style="text-align:right;"><p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="tt" href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http://popdigital.ca/2011/05/15/countrywide-communications/&text=Website%3A+Countrywide+Communications&via=tweetthisplugin&related=richardxthripp%2Ctweetthisplugin" title="Post to Twitter"><img class="nothumb" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/plugins/tweet-this/icons/en/twitter/tt-twitter6.png" alt="Post to Twitter" /></a></p></div>
